How to Use:
Sign up / Login on the home page.
Go to /vault.
Enter a master password and click Derive Key (used to encrypt/decrypt locally).
Use password generator to create a secure password; click generate to populate the create form.
Save item â†’ server stores only encrypted blob.
Click Reveal on a saved item to decrypt locally (requires derived key).
Click Copy to copy password; clipboard clears automatically after ~10s.
